{"tid":1654101,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"如果你睇到既片，以為有個日既時間就以為係個日","createTime":"2019-10-14T12:02:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T12:12:21.000Z","uid":5890,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7b81cbbf361f6516b53a2e886ad379baca19eb21","tid":1654101,"uid":5890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T12:02:15.000Z","msg":"如果你睇到既片，以為有個日既時間就以為係個日，咁就中晒計<br />\n<br />\n會唔會係隔便搵一日既片，再將時間改做個日。改比你睇，你點睇都查唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad77c34335e702f9f73f2fe0352ce77a97374322","tid":1654101,"uid":5890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T12:04:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d08bd5c3c48a5696b6579b781931e3dd86904b5","tid":1654101,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T12:07:32.000Z","msg":"無錯"},{"pid":"951093dee03312fa44b25505205e660c08cf31a7","tid":1654101,"uid":35604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T12:08:00.000Z","msg":"其實off機改左時間開機再錄你都唔會知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f95859b7f7f957dd7c962a3781b92eb674e2f1b","tid":1654101,"uid":5890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d08bd5c3c48a5696b6579b781931e3dd86904b5","tid":1654101,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T12:07:32.000Z","msg":"無錯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T12:09:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以一段蒙到咁撚樣既片，根本無用<br />\n係唔係個日都無人知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9617dc8144a2aa3e4fe24f0db3e7bf592e47eea","tid":1654101,"uid":169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T12:0